    <header>
        <h1>MIS Errors Catalog</h1>
        <p>A repository of documented MIS errors for the California Community College system (Banner)</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>This page catalogs common MIS errors encountered within the California Community College system for Banner. Each entry provides the error code, description, potential causes, and solutions.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Error List</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h3>Error Code: <code>ED001</code></h3>
                    <p><strong>Description:</strong> Missing or invalid student enrollment status.</p>
                    <p><strong>Potential Causes:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Incorrect status code entered.</li>
                        <li>Missing enrollment record in the current term.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Verify the student's enrollment status and update the Banner record under the <code>SGASTDN</code> form.</p>
                </li>

                <li>
                    <h3>Error Code: <code>SCFF001</code></h3>
                    <p><strong>Description:</strong> Invalid financial aid disbursement data.</p>
                    <p><strong>Potential Causes:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Mismatched student ID in financial aid records.</li>
                        <li>Missing Pell or AB540 status for applicable students.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Cross-check financial aid data in the <code>RPAAWRD</code> form and ensure SCFF eligibility fields are populated correctly.</p>
                </li>

                <!-- Add more errors here -->
            </ul>
        </section>
